>\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一步一步黎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc18b3d51edb16ad79615f8fe9b7697afe4f089","tid":347920,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該好返 依家無再流鼻水鼻涕<br />\n但個眼圈仲喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無啲中醫推介？<br />\n即係都會認同同識做中藥美容既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問你點醫鼻竇炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我小三既時候開始睇專科 食藥去到小四 <br />\n之後好返 但有次感冒 又返發<br />\n之後又再食藥 食到小五六<br />\n之後嫌煩就無再食<br />\n<br />\n中學都一路流黃綠鼻涕 返學都帶一卷紙巾<br />\n後來屋企人帶我返大陸睇<br />\n屌 佢成支棉花隊入去<br />\n痛到我大喊 之後無再搞<br />\n但又好似慢慢無再流<br />\n<br />\n升左yr1 基本上都無再流<br />\n所以我都唔肯定係個大陸「醫生」定乜"}]}